one_reviews_text: this game is really well done the touch controls are  perfect and this game really shows them off . its simple yet addictive ; the gameplay gets pretty deep to hit  a high score and get on leader board

review_title: Very Fun and good game with my friends!!
one_reviews_text:
Good Stuff, I Like This Game!!
and with my friends this game, very fun XD
Don't know why, but I find this game addictive in Touch mode. The addiction paid off and I'm currently ranking number 1 on the Touch Global Leaderboard. 0.o
With family, friends and beer, it's the best VR game. The most important thing is not dizziness.
